featured_reviews.review_id: Handmade dumplings that are equally delicious steamed, boiled, and pan-fried! The shape is perfect for catching whatever sauce you want to toss them in.

featured_reviews.review_id: We ordered 5 bags of Dicky's dumplings, shrimps and scallops, and veggies. We have also tried the ginger chicken, and pork and chives. They are very high quality and taste great

featured_reviews.review_id:
We rate Dicky's Dumps 10/10, 5 stars, A+++!
Ordering and communication was easy, delivery was delightful.... Had a lovely conversation with Dickson, who truly cares about their business and their product!....
Oh, and their  'dumps' were delicious!! Yummm!
Enjoyed the vegetarian ones.... They are tasty!!
Will definitely buy them again. Treat yourself!!
